platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Puzzles to make your head spin

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: FEZ begins with a simple idea: you can rotate the world. The more you play, the more you understand this concepts far-reaching implications as you jump between ledges and rotate perspective to get pieces of the world to align. The complexity and sophistication of the puzzles keeps growing, building on ideas and forcing you to think in new ways. FEZ is perfect for anyone who loves scouring every little corner of virtual spaces for hidden secrets.
